Dialogue: 5,0:00:01.08,0:00:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think my dad could stand\N the fact that he was labeled a thief.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:06.01,0:00:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And my mom apparently thought he really did steal.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:12.06,0:00:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost lost my faith in humanity.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:15.17,0:00:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I even thought that maybe I'd feel better if I grew to hate one of my parents.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:21.05,0:00:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But years later,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:23.59,0:00:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard my mom regret not believing him back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:29.35,0:00:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when I realized I should continue to love them both.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:37.38,0:00:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that my belief in people was one of my good points.
