Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.99,0:02:11.99,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:14.79,0:02:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-What the hell?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.87,0:02:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Airi enter the house earlier!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:19.12,0:02:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Could she still be inside?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:21.56,0:02:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.77,0:02:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Airi!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:27.95,0:02:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Airi?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.76,0:02:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Airi!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:38.04,0:02:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Airi!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:40.30,0:02:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:49.50,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't carry her!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Airi!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.44,0:03:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.04,0:03:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way I can do this alone!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.54,0:03:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.45,0:03:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Never depend on a manga artist.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.71,0:03:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going down at once!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.87,0:03:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Steady now!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.64,0:03:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru, go out the back.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.98,0:03:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get Airi mixed up in this anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.97,0:03:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be taking all the credit.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will Airi be okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.64,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that fire...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.58,0:03:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me he was behind it as well.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.54,0:03:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, right.
