Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.81,0:04:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That fire was deliberately lit to kill Airi.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.24,0:04:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it was set up to look like I did it.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.22,0:04:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Airi snuck her phone into my pocket so the police wouldn't see this text.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.52,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This means the killer already knew Airi's address or followed her.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.67,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He might be right under my nose.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.99,0:04:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to look for him.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.24,0:04:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a race to see whether I get caught first or find him first.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Koiwa, Koiwa.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.34,0:04:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please be sure not to leave anything—
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.83,0:04:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.18,0:04:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.39,0:04:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Introduce yourself already.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.86,0:04:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Fujinuma Satoru.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.30,0:04:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really are Fujinuma Satoru, then it's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.54,0:04:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for your call.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.63,0:04:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, by all means.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.66,0:04:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's meet in public.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.16,0:04:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I haven't introduced myself yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.08,0:04:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's save that for when we meet tomorrow.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:00.82,0:05:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you might be the one\N who murdered Fujinuma Sachiko.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.59,0:05:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.62,0:05:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Satoru. Over here.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.87,0:05:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.13,0:05:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The name's Sawada. I used to work for the TV Ishikari city desk.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are Satoru.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:22.89,0:05:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You resemble your mother, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:27.40,0:05:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's him.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.73,0:05:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you came here on full alert, but I didn't tip off the cops.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.36,0:05:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor did I murder your mother.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.59,0:05:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you suspect me?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.72,0:05:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:39.14,0:05:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:41.70,0:05:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she wouldn't raise a son who'd kill her.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.41,0:05:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered that I had it in my pocket yesterday.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.40,0:05:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This has become quite the fiasco.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.36,0:05:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no excuse.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.17,0:06:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is partly my fault for screwing up so many times in a row.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:00.88,0:06:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's conceited to blame yourself for somethin' after it happens.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.16,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As Sachiko used to put it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I always liked that phrase.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.46,0:06:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we talk about the phone call I got from her?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.67,0:06:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.84,0:06:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawada, do you remember the serial murder case from 18 years ago?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.82,0:06:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.87,0:06:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiratori Jun is on death row\N and still hasn't admitted his guilt.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.58,0:06:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Satoru was right.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.79,0:06:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shiratori didn't do it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.53,0:06:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I know who the real culprit is.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.73,0:06:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's meet at Koiwa Station tomorrow.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.58,0:06:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've asked for a name.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.92,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about something that happened in the past:
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the Hinazuki Kayo murder.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.71,0:06:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,On the night of March 2nd, 1988,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.66,0:07:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kayo was locked in the shed after being beaten by her mother and her mother's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.61,0:07:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She froze to death.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.63,0:07:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, the police suspected the two adults,\N thinking they'd hid the body.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.84,0:07:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But in reality, Kayo had disappeared from\N the shed between 10 and 11 PM on the 2nd.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.46,0:07:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When her mother noticed she \Nwas gone at 12:30 AM on the 3rd,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.38,0:07:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,she quietly began looking for her and called the Fujinumas.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.16,0:07:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Shiratori Jun who had kidnapped her.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.47,0:07:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,One piece of evidence provided was the rubber boot footprints near the shed.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.92,0:07:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They matched perfectly with boots found at the Shiratori home.
