Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.76,0:07:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He knocked her out with blunt force, photographed her,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.45,0:07:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and then took her to a commercial freezer, \Nwhere he used an atomizer to speed up her death.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.12,0:07:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment her body temperature dropped to 20 degrees, she was brain dead.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.67,0:07:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He then waited 30 minutes to erase all possibility of her remaining alive
Dialogue: 5,0:07:57.01,0:08:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and took the corpse back to the Hinazuki shed before sunrise.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yuuki would never do something like that!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.65,0:08:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A little before Hinazuki Kayo, Sugita Hiromi, and Nakanishi Aya disappeared,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.68,0:08:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a kidnapping-cum-murder case in the next town over too.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:18.26,0:08:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit was caught immediately, \Nand just like Shiratori, they denied any wrongdoing.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.65,0:08:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:25.07,0:08:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,if we also take your current situation into account,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.55,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't a certain realization strike you?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.59,0:08:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been ridiculed for years as a crazy reporter who investigates already solved cases.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.10,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But not one of them has actually been solved.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.07,0:08:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Hinazuki Kayo and Sachiko were murdered by someone who frames others for his crimes!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:47.04,0:08:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's in this city right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:49.84,0:08:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's one devious son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.14,0:08:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,By framing others, he delays investigations to \Na point where eyewitnesses dwindle in number
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.33,0:08:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and crime scenes are no longer preserved in their exact state.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.28,0:09:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, the trail goes cold.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:14.48,0:09:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Talk about overreacting.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.76,0:09:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So he tried to silence her?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that Fujinuma Satoru.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.72,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't interrogate her now.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.57,0:09:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But more importantly, what about her own involvement?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.78,0:09:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She could be an accomplice.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:29.14,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he forced her to help him kill his mother, and once he didn't need her anymore, he tried to silence her for good.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.95,0:09:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How awful.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.55,0:09:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he dragged a young girl into his crimes.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.02,0:09:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're wrong.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.11,0:09:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for you to apologize, Airi.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:42.81,0:09:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was all that stalker's fault, not yours.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've been so scared.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it, Aunty.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:50.15,0:09:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine! Sorry we didn't realize.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're wrong.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.34,0:09:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The police are chasing the culprit.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.85,0:09:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.11,0:10:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you've got it all wrong.
