Dialogue: 5,0:10:12.25,0:10:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe Satoru's being hunted for murder and arson.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.56,0:10:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But who would be willing to believe us?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.53,0:10:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl got a text from Sachiko's phone?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.44,0:10:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.52,0:10:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the news, she only suffered light injuries, but she's probably still in the hospital.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.99,0:10:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's her phone.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:40.20,0:10:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.54,0:10:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He tried to speed up the murder investigation by framing you for arson as well.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.15,0:10:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's partly why, \Nbut I was already the prime suspect.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.53,0:10:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he'd go after her, \NKatagiri Airi, for just that reason.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.69,0:10:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying she was a target herself?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.33,0:11:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to frame me for my mother's murder,\N he needed to know when I'd get home from work.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.55,0:11:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed her a little more than a day after she witnessed his kidnapping attempt.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.60,0:11:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In that timeframe, he visited the\N pizza shop and saw the shift schedule.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.49,0:11:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And Airi must've seen him then.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.77,0:11:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He might even be someone I know.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.29,0:11:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. To check the schedule, \Nhe must've had staff area access.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.65,0:11:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We might just be able to catch him.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.47,0:11:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll head to the hospital.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.52,0:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:34.80,0:11:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There are reports on the murders \Nfrom 18 years ago on my computer.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.26,0:11:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to take a look.
