Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.05,0:13:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The killer's name must be on it!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.59,0:13:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Katagiri, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.55,0:13:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm here to visit. But first, is the restroom that way?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.34,0:13:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.54,0:13:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No vacancies...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.91,0:13:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And only room 201 is empty.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sleeping.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.29,0:13:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.26,0:13:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! I'm gonna wet myself!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.39,0:13:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon my intrusion, Katagiri Airi.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.25,0:13:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not Fujinuma Satoru, are you?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:59.94,0:14:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right. I'm his friend, Sawada.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.60,0:14:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.11,0:14:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Airi's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:13.00,ep number,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1021,224)\c&H1F16C8&\blur0.5}Episode {\fnFranklin Gothic Demi}6
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:13.00,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,95)\c&H181924&\blur0.55}Reaper
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.00,0:14:13.00,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.71,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way Satoru could've done it.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.58,0:14:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he could've killed \Nhis mother or tried to burn me alive.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.36,0:14:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He actually came to save me from the fire!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.93,0:14:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your manager was the one who saved you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.69,0:14:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Inhaling all that smoke must've messed with your memory.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:29.48,0:14:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you've heard,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.31,0:14:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but they think I could be his accomplice!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.44,0:14:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts me so much that nobody believes me.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.36,0:14:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But people are even less likely to believe Satoru, \Nand that hurts me more.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:44.72,0:14:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Airi,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.50,0:14:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I still feel I should've gone after your father.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.36,0:14:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So off you go.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.00,0:14:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I believe you.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.88,0:15:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! I forgot to turn it off!
