Dialogue: 5,0:15:19.65,0:15:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was still on! Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Airi?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.40,0:15:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.58,0:15:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.66,0:15:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That aside, can we meet at the usual place now?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.60,0:15:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stay away!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.75,0:15:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, they'll susp—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.81,0:15:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's all good!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.90,0:15:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I swear I'll come alone!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.41,0:15:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it actually gonna fly?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.40,0:15:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe I actually came.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:45.76,0:15:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should've just asked her about the killer over the phone.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:49.79,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'll only make things worse for her if she gets involved any further.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.83,0:15:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.34,0:15:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't fly at all!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:59.08,0:16:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.52,0:16:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't it fly?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.00,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to do this to give it something called aerodynamic lift.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.72,0:16:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Will that really make it fly?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.22,0:16:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:14.68,0:16:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! You're right!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It flew toward the river!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:20.16,0:16:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's flying too far!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:20.98,0:16:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he doing here at this hour?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he unemployed?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.69,0:16:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.41,0:16:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did Mr. Yuuki go through this too?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.77,0:17:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am, Satoru.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.03,0:17:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.86,0:17:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I came alone, just as promised!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.64,0:17:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed of myself for thinking this could be a police trap.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I said that out loud.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:17.43,0:17:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn well should have, too!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.52,0:17:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a fugitive, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.60,0:17:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm happy you believed in me.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.04,0:17:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:28.48,0:17:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The pizza shop?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.14,0:17:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This Nishizono man is the most suspicious, I think.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.74,0:17:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishizono?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:33.78,0:17:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen him two or three times.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.38,0:17:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The manager's all respectful around him, \Nand he wears a badge, so he's probably a city councilor.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.96,0:17:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He would've been able to check the schedule,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.77,0:17:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and it wouldn't be out of the question for him to know where we live.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.44,0:17:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've even exchanged pleasantries with him.
