Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nishizono?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.77,0:17:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't see that name on the list.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:50.57,0:17:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An alias?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.73,0:17:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But surely you can't sit on the city council under an alias.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.60,0:17:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably tried to kill me because I knew his face.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:57.90,0:18:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit! It isn't coming together!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:00.65,0:18:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final piece of the puzzle won't fit!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.06,0:18:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel, but don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:08.57,0:18:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I have unfinished business from a long time ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.08,0:18:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm talking about a manga I came up with.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.25,0:18:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story about a reaper who gets his \Ntiming wrong and ends up killing a child.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.97,0:18:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He tries desperately to undo his mistake,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.73,0:18:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but the more he tries, the more misfortune he brings to the people he comes in contact with.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.36,0:18:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to do the right thing,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:31.66,0:18:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but everything he does hurts other people.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.27,0:18:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean to say he's like you right now?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.17,0:18:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.89,0:18:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, stupid?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:45.38,0:18:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For one, I didn't get hurt.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.06,0:18:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And that stuff about others was just the reaper jumping to conclusions.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:50.26,0:18:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that reaper needs to believe in himself more.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:54.50,0:18:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that's happening right now is just work in progress.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.03,0:19:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The ending is a ways off, and nobody can see it yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.47,0:19:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so lucky to have met you, Airi.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I said that out loud!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Fujinuma Satoru, correct?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.60,0:19:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.64,0:19:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Airi!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.07,0:19:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujinuma Satoru,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:26.19,0:19:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you're under arrest on charges of murder \Nand attempted murder resulting from arson.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:36.11,0:19:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Suspect apprehended at 1650 hours.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.51,0:19:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru didn't do it!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:42.45,0:19:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he could have!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.70,0:19:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew that my relationship with Airi would cease to exist, either via arrest or Revival.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:51.71,0:19:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that time has come. I'll never see her again.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:55.53,0:19:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What I'm supposed to do right now is...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.06,0:19:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Satoru!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:59.45,0:20:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably led these people here,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:03.27,0:20:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,even though I promised to come alone!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.29,0:20:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to give Airi what I wanted to.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.00,0:20:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Repay her for what she did for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.77,0:20:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:17.05,0:20:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:19.69,0:20:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would a superhero say at a time like this?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:26.81,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it painful to fight all alone?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong, Airi.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.59,0:20:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you believed in me that I can keep fighting.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.26,0:20:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Airi.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:44.48,0:20:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I believed in you.
